{"id": "art-352", "label": "Art. 352", "title": "Art. 352: Publicitatea şedinţei de judecată", "slug": "art-352", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 352: Publicitatea &#351;edin&#355;ei de judecat&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)&#350;edin&#355;a de\njudecat&#259; este public&#259;, cu excep&#355;ia cazurilor prev&#259;zute de\nlege. &#350;edin&#355;a desf&#259;&#351;urat&#259; în camera de consiliu nu\neste public&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Nu pot asista la\n&#351;edin&#355;a de judecat&#259; minorii sub 18 ani, cu excep&#355;ia\nsitua&#355;iei în care ace&#351;tia au calitatea de p&#259;r&#355;i sau\nmartori, precum &#351;i persoanele înarmate, cu excep&#355;ia personalului care\nasigur&#259; paza &#351;i ordinea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; judecarea în\n&#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259; ar putea aduce atingere unor interese de\nstat, moralei, demnit&#259;&#355;ii sau vie&#355;ii intime a unei persoane,\nintereselor minorilor sau ale justi&#355;iei, instan&#355;a, la cererea procurorului,\na p&#259;r&#355;ilor ori din oficiu, poate declara &#351;edin&#355;&#259;\nnepublic&#259; pentru tot cursul sau pentru o anumit&#259; parte a\njudec&#259;rii cauzei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_267747097\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1808\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_267747097\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>1</sup>)Din oficiu sau la solicitarea expres&#259; a\npersoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate sau a procurorului, &#351;edin&#355;a de\njudecat&#259; este declarat&#259; nepublic&#259; pentru tot cursul s&#259;u\ndac&#259; persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259; este minor&#259; &#351;i este\nvictima uneia dintre infrac&#355;iunile prev&#259;zute la art. 197, 199,\n209-216<sup>1</sup>, 218, 218<sup>1</sup>, 219, 219<sup>1</sup>, 221, 222, 223\n&#351;i 374 din </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul penal</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_603080652\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1807\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_603080652\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>2</sup>)La solicitarea expres&#259; a persoanei\nv&#259;t&#259;mate sau a procurorului, &#351;edin&#355;a de judecat&#259; este\ndeclarat&#259; nepublic&#259; pentru tot cursul s&#259;u dac&#259; judecarea în\n&#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259; ar putea aduce atingere unor interese de\nstat, moralei, demnit&#259;&#355;ii sau vie&#355;ii intime a unei persoane.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Instan&#355;a poate de asemenea\ns&#259; declare &#351;edin&#355;&#259; nepublic&#259; la cererea unui martor,\ndac&#259; prin audierea sa în &#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259; s-ar aduce\natingere siguran&#355;ei ori demnit&#259;&#355;ii sau vie&#355;ii intime a\nacestuia sau a membrilor familiei sale, ori la cererea procurorului, a\npersoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate sau a p&#259;r&#355;ilor, în cazul în care o\naudiere în public ar pune în pericol confiden&#355;ialitatea unor\ninforma&#355;ii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Declararea &#351;edin&#355;ei\nnepublice se face în &#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259;, dup&#259; ascultarea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor prezente, a persoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate &#351;i a\nprocurorului. Dispozi&#355;ia instan&#355;ei este executorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(6)În timpul cât &#351;edin&#355;a\neste nepublic&#259;, nu sunt admise în sala de &#351;edin&#355;&#259; decât\np&#259;r&#355;ile, persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;, reprezentan&#355;ii\nacestora, avoca&#355;ii &#351;i celelalte persoane a c&#259;ror prezen&#355;&#259;\neste autorizat&#259; de instan&#355;&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1604668678\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1806\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1604668678\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)P&#259;r&#355;ile, persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;,\nreprezentan&#355;ii acestora, avoca&#355;ii &#351;i exper&#355;ii\ndesemna&#355;i în cauz&#259; au dreptul de a lua cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259; de\nactele &#351;i con&#355;inutul dosarului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1310475886\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1805\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1310475886\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Pre&#351;edintele completului are îndatorirea de a aduce\nla cuno&#351;tin&#355;a persoanelor ce particip&#259; la judecata\ndesf&#259;&#351;urat&#259; în &#351;edin&#355;&#259; nepublic&#259;\nobliga&#355;ia de a p&#259;stra confiden&#355;ialitatea informa&#355;iilor\nob&#355;inute pe parcursul procesului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(9)Pe durata judec&#259;&#355;ii,\ninstan&#355;a poate interzice publicarea &#351;i difuzarea, prin mijloace\nscrise sau audiovizuale, de texte, desene, fotografii sau imagini de\nnatur&#259; a dezv&#259;lui identitatea persoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate, a p&#259;r&#355;ii\ncivile, a p&#259;r&#355;ii responsabile civilmente sau a martorilor, în\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (3) sau (4).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_70438184\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1804\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_70438184\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Informa&#355;iile de interes public din dosar se\ncomunic&#259; în condi&#355;iile legii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_793014303\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1803\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_793014303\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1667376910\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1802\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1667376910\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>[textul din Art. 352, alin. (11) din partea 2, titlul III,\ncapitolul I a fost abrogat la 09-iul-2023 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art.\nI, punctul 41. din Legea 201/2023</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_363638582\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1801\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_363638582\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(12)</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_298635262\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1800\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_298635262\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>[textul din Art. 352, alin. (12) din partea 2, titlul III,\ncapitolul I a fost abrogat la 09-iul-2023 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art.\nI, punctul 41. din Legea 201/2023</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>"}